      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that gets the job done? This vehicle is a solid, practical choice for anyone needing dependable transportation! While it shows some honest wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a sturdy companion ready for many more miles. It's a fantastic opportunity to own a functional car at a very accessible price point!",
